      "message": "madd have big latency, as the other multiply instructions.\n\nAlso found this layout, but it doesn\u0027t work faster, despite that there are even fewer instructions:\n\n  const __m128i mult \u003d MK_CST_16(CST_5b(red_to_blue) + 256,\n                                 CST_5b(green_to_blue));\n\n      const __m128i A1 \u003d _mm_loadu_si128((const __m128i*)\u0026src[x + 0]);\n      const __m128i A2 \u003d _mm_loadu_si128((const __m128i*)\u0026src[x + 4]);\n      const __m128i B1 \u003d _mm_shuffle_epi8(A1, perm);\n      const __m128i B2 \u003d _mm_shuffle_epi8(A2, perm);\n      const __m128i C1 \u003d _mm_mulhi_epi16(B1, mult);\n      const __m128i C2 \u003d _mm_mulhi_epi16(B2, mult);\n      const __m128i X1 \u003d _mm_sub_epi16(A1, C1);\n      const __m128i X2 \u003d _mm_sub_epi16(A2, C2);\n      const __m128i D \u003d _mm_hadd_epi16(X1, X2);",
